ariba.ui.validation
Class AWVFormatterFactory

java.lang.Object
  ariba.ui.validation.AWVFormatterFactory

public final class AWVFormatterFactory
extends Object

Provides a default (localized) set of formatters accessible via "$formatters.{name}" bindings off of AWComponents.

Bundled formatters include:

  1. boolean
  2. integer
  3. long
  4. double
  5. bigDecimal
  6. money
  7. shortDate
  8. longDate
  9. dateTime
  10. longDateTime
  11. shortAbsoluteDate
  12. longAbsoluteDate
  13. absoluteDateTime
  14. longAbsoluteDateTime
  15. duration
  16. timeMillis
  17. hiddenPassword
